After adding a .q file you generate the .q.out file via:

{noformat}
cd itests
mvn test -Dtest=TestCliDriver -Dqfile=my_parquet.q -Dtest.output.overwrite=true -Phadoop-2
{noformat}

https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/Hive/HiveDeveloperFAQ#HiveDeveloperFAQ-HowdoIupdatetheoutputofaCliDrivertestcase?
